## Data model

### Community (project-specific)

Key fields (non-exhaustive; see `community.schema.ts`):

| Field | Role |
|-------|------|
| `isProject`, `typeTag: 'project'` | Identify project community |
| `projectDuration`, `projectStatus` | Lifecycle |
| `founderUserId`, `founderSharePercent`, `investorSharePercent` | Cooperative + default Birzha invest % |
| `parentCommunityId` | Link to parent (ОБ / team); optional |
| `communityWalletId` | Wallet document |
| `futureVisionText`, `futureVisionTags`, `futureVisionCover` | Parent ОБ-style metadata where used |
| `rejectionMessage` | Neutral ticket rejection copy |
| `settings.investingEnabled` | Under `Community.settings` (not a top-level Community field). `project.create` maps input `investingEnabled` here; project wallet invest / payout code reads `project.settings?.investingEnabled`. |

### Publication (inside project or Birzha-bound)

| Field | Role |
|-------|------|
| `postType` | In a project community: `'ticket' \| 'discussion'` required (enforced when `community.isProject`); elsewhere includes `basic`, `poll`, legacy `project` |
| `ticketStatus`, `isNeutralTicket`, `applicants`, `deadline` | Ticket workflow |
| `sourceEntityId`, `sourceEntityType` | Link to project or community for Birzha / context posts |
| `beneficiaryId` | Optional; immutable on create when set |

### CommunityWallet

| Field | Role |
|-------|------|
| `communityId` | Project (or source) id |
| `balance` | Operational: top-up, `postCost`, tappalka show cost from wallet |
| `totalReceived`, `totalDistributed` | `deposit` increments **`balance`** and **`totalReceived`**; **`debit`** (payout from wallet) decrements **`balance`** and increments **`totalDistributed`**; **`addTotalDistributed`** increments only **`totalDistributed`** (transit helper; used by `ProjectDistributionService` when that path runs) |

### Membership

`UserCommunityRole`: `role` `'lead' | 'participant'`; `frozenInternalMerits` when member leaves with frozen share.

