## Notifications

Types present in `notification.schema.ts` for this domain (subset; see file for full union):

| Type | Typical trigger |
|------|-----------------|
| `project_created` | Project created (parent lead / context) |
| `ticket_assigned`, `ticket_done`, `ticket_accepted`, `ticket_evaluated`, `ticket_returned_for_revision`, `ticket_assignee_declined` | Ticket lifecycle |
| `project_published` | Published to Birzha |
| `project_distributed` | After **`ProjectPayoutService`** credits (wallet payout / sweep); same type is also emitted inside **`ProjectDistributionService.distribute`** if that path runs |
| `project_closed` | Project archived / close |
| `member_joined`, `member_left_project` | Membership |
| `shares_changed` | Founder share update **or** admin transfer (metadata may carry `transferAdmin`) |
| `ticket_apply`, `ticket_rejection` | Neutral ticket applications |
| `ob_vote_join_offer` | First vote on ОБ post (future-vision) |
| `project_parent_link_requested`, `project_parent_link_approved`, `project_parent_link_rejected` | Parent link workflow |

Investor messaging on close may include **project name** prefix in `PostClosingService` notifications (investment types: see @business-investing.mdc).

