## UI behavior notes

- App routes live under **`/meriter/projects`** (not bare `/projects`).  
- **Publish to Birzha** from UI: navigates to **`/meriter/projects/[id]/birzha-publish`** (not only an inline dialog).  
- Legacy **`postType === 'project'`** in non-project communities is gated by **`ENABLE_PROJECT_POSTS`** (`web` constants) — **currently `false`**; cooperative projects use **communities + ticket/discussion**, not this legacy path.  
- **Top-up** dialog stresses donation vs investment where applicable.

