## Dependencies

```
Community (isProject)
  ├── UserCommunityRole (lead/participant, frozenInternalMerits)
  ├── CommunityWalletService
  ├── TicketService + publications (ticket/discussion)
  ├── project.publishToBirzha → Publication in МД (sourceEntityType project)
  ├── publications.withdraw / PostClosingService → CommunityWallet.deposit (source entity)
  ├── ProjectPayoutService (wallet sweep; project + eligible non-project sources)
  └── TappalkaService (show cost from project wallet when source is project)

Related:
  InvestmentService (investor slice) → then authorShare to CommunityWallet for МД Birzha source posts
  ProjectDistributionService (unused from routers; tests only)
  Future-vision / ОБ (sourceEntityType community) — separate wallet path
```

